SARS - WORLDWIDE (140): CASES
*****************************
A ProMED-mail post
<http://www.promedmail.org>
ProMED-mail is a program of the
International Society for Infectious Diseases
<http://www.isid.org>
[Note: as SARS activity has been decreasing, many of the official
websites are not posting updates on the weekends (Saturday and
Sunday). ProMED-mail will continue to monitor official websites and
post material as it becomes available. ProMED-mail will also monitor
newswire reports, but will continue to exercise prudence in posting
from newswires, as many "suspected" cases reported through newswires
are later found to have other etiologies. - Mod. MPP]
