[There were 7 new probable cases reported in Ontario for 7 Jun 2003
with 2 new deaths. Information on the dates of onset of the newly
reported cases was not available in order to determine whether these
are newly occurring cases or delayed identification of cases. Taiwan
reported 3 new probable cases since yesterday's update. The date of
onset of most recent reported case in Taiwan is 7 Jun 2003. There
were no new probable cases reported from China or Hong Kong. -
Mod.MPP]
